description: 1500-test end-to-end chaos suite for production safety validation

test_classes.name: spelling_errors
test_classes.purpose: Test fuzzy matching and typo tolerance
test_classes.expected_behavior: Should still find relevant results or return UNKNOWN_OK

test_classes.name: abbreviations
test_classes.purpose: Test marine abbreviations (ME, DG, P/S, stbd, etc.)

test_classes.name: voice_dictation
test_classes.purpose: Test voice-to-text style queries (run-on, no punctuation)
test_classes.expected_behavior: Should understand intent despite run-on style

test_classes.name: multi_intent_collision
test_classes.purpose: Test queries with multiple conflicting intents
test_classes.expected_behavior: Should pick primary intent or return disambiguation

test_classes.name: command_camouflage
test_classes.expected_behavior: Should detect command despite politeness wrapping

test_classes.name: politeness_drift
test_classes.purpose: Test gradual drift from polite request to command

test_classes.name: suffix_noise
test_classes.purpose: Test queries with trailing noise (thanks, please, etc.)

test_classes.name: entity_soup
test_classes.purpose: Test many entities with no clear verb
test_classes.expected_behavior: Should search for entities, not assume action

test_classes.name: angry_urgent
test_classes.expected_behavior: Should extract intent despite emotion, detect urgency

test_classes.name: injection_realistic
test_classes.purpose: Test injection hidden in marine context

test_classes.name: equipment_faults
test_classes.expected_behavior: Should extract both equipment and symptom

test_classes.name: work_order_intents
test_classes.expected_behavior: Should detect intent but capability is blocked

test_classes.name: fault_code_lookups
test_classes.expected_behavior: Should extract fault code and route correctly

test_classes.name: manufacturer_models
test_classes.expected_behavior: Should extract manufacturer and model entities

test_classes.name: temporal_context
test_classes.purpose: Test time-related queries (before charter, last week)

test_classes.name: action_chains
test_classes.purpose: Test chained actions (find then create, check then order)

test_classes.name: edge_cases
test_classes.purpose: Test empty, single char, unicode, emoji
